SUMMARY:Penn & Teller Celebrate 50 Years of Magic + Pre-lunch (Union Stati
 on)
DESCRIPTION:Experience Toronto\nOn **Saturday June 6th**\, **let's Celebra
 te 50 Years of Magic with Penn & Teller.** Penn & Teller return to Toronto
  for the first time in 16 years with an unforgettable night of mind-blowin
 g illusions\, sharp wit\, and legendary showmanship. Penn & Teller are a l
 egendary magic act - Emmy\, Obie\, and Writer’s Guild Award-winning\, wi
 th stars on the Hollywood Walk of Fame. Penn & Teller know magic. Their CW
  TV show “Penn & Teller: Fool Us” has launched countless magic careers
 \, while successful Broadway runs and sold-out overseas tours have secured
  their place in the history books. My seat is ORCH10\, Row A\, Seat 83. **
 Please Purchase the newly added show on June 6th at 2pm show and post your
  seat number (caution there are other dates and times)**\n\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\
 -\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\
 \-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\n**REGULAR COST**
 \nTickets: $69 to $199 + ticket master fees\n\nOrganizer Meetup fee: $5\n\
 nTicket Policy: Final Sale - Non-Refundable & Non-Exchangeable. (You may o
 pt to buy their insurance\, if you so desire.)\n\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-
 \\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\
 -\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\n**SIGNING-UP**\n\n* **RSVP
  Yes and answer the question about Lunch\, and the system will add you to 
 the waitlist.**\n* **[Purchase your ticket](https://www.ticketmaster.ca/ev
 ent/1000642FAD44DCCB?brand=tolive&CAMEFROM=CFC_TOLIVE_EMAIL_TOLIVE_E1&utm_
 source=TO+Live&utm_campaign=e0f9025468-EMAIL_CAMPAIGN_2026_01_19_04_29&utm
 _medium=email&utm_term=0_-e0f9025468-584141646&mc_cid=e0f9025468&mc_eid=96
 e408c1f2)**[ ](https://www.stratfordfestival.ca/WhatsOn/Calendar)and post 
 your seat number\, so others may sit next to you.\n* I will then move you 
 to attending\n\nRSVPs close 1 day prior and cancellations after may result
  in a No Show and impact future attendance.\n\nA reminder will be sent the
  day before with my cell and details where to meet and when.\n\n**MEETUP T
 IME**\n**Meet me for lunch at: 12pm inside the front doors of restaurant T
 BC at 33 Yonge St\,** Please wait for me to arrive\, and do not sit on you
 r own prior\, so we can get the table requested.\n\n**Meet me for the show
  at 1:30pm** inside the 2nd set of glass front doors of Meridian Hall at 1
  Front St. E. to the right side\, after scanning your tickets. We will aim
  to be in our seats 15 mins prior to catch an early start\n\n**Show start 
 time: 2pm**\n\nShow length: estimate 90 mins\, there may be some interacti
 on before and after\, per their website\, so arrive early\n\nEnjoy and ple
 ase post your Comments in the event after.
